Package smarthome.persistence.jpa

Class DeviceRepositoryJPAImpl

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.jpa.DeviceRepositoryJPAImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<DeviceId, Device>, IDeviceRepository
public class DeviceRepositoryJPAImpl extends Object implements IDeviceRepository
Device Repository JPA This class provides an implementation of the IDeviceRepository interface using Java Persistence API (JPA) for database operations. It interacts with the database to perform CRUD operations on Device entities.

    • update

      public Device update (Device device)
      Updates a Device entity in the repository. It retrieves the DeviceDataModel entity by its identity from the database. If the entity exists, it updates the DeviceDataModel entity from the Device domain object and merges it to the database. The method returns the updated Device entity. If the entity does not exist, it returns null.
      Specified by:

      Parameters:

      Returns:
